title: Chadwick Johnson from Hundredth
itunes:title: Chadwick Johnson from Hundredth
description:
Let's do this! We have a return guest with Chadwick Johnson from Hundredth, who just released an incredible new LP called "Somewhere Nowhere." We discuss the band as a brand, evolution in a band's sound and keeping everything very DIY. It was a great catch up discussion and enjoy the hang time.
